			"9. ERROR in X.java (at line 14)\n" + 
			"	public static <E> void eachWithIndex(List<E> list, ItemWithIndexVisitor<E> visitor) {\n" + 
			"	                                                                        ^\n" + 
			"Syntax error, parameterized types are only available if source level is 1.5 or greater\n" + 
